body_html: As of version .12, tf.strided_slice has [misleading documentation](https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/master/api_docs/python/array_ops/slicing_and_joining#strided_slice). A fourth argument is mandatory, not a keyword argument, and it cannot be None.
body_text: As of version .12, tf.strided_slice has [misleading documentation](https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/master/api_docs/python/array_ops/slicing_and_joining#strided_slice).  A fourth argument is mandatory, not a keyword argument, and it cannot be None.
body: As of version .12, `tf.strided_slice` has `[misleading documentation](https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/master/api_docs/python/array_ops/slicing_and_joining#strided_slice)`.  A fourth argument is mandatory, not a keyword argument, and it cannot be `None`.
